        <p class="c6"><span class="c1">What is App Deployment?</span></p>
        <p class="c6">
            <span class="c2">
                App deployment is the process of making an application available for use. It involves several steps, including preparing
                the app for release, transferring it to a production environment, and configuring it to ensure it runs smoothly.
                Effective app deployment is crucial for ensuring that users can access and use the app without issues.
            </span>
        </p>

